subsection.def:
immobilisation device (鎖車設備) means any device or appliance designed or
                adapted to be fitted to a vehicle for the purpose of preventing it from being driven
                or otherwise put in motion;

road marking (道路標記) means a line, word, mark or device placed on, or set into, the
                surface of a private road for conveying to persons using that road any warning,
                information, requirement, restriction, prohibition or direction;

